    "Poe is a platform developed by Quora that allows users to interact with various AI models, including ChatGPT.",
    "It provides a user-friendly interface for accessing different chatbots, enabling users to explore AI capabilities in conversational contexts.",
    "While ChatGPT is developed by OpenAI, Poe serves as a medium through which users can engage with it and other models.",
    "For this study, we followed the procedure described below to create a conversational tutor bot using ChatGPT to conduct tutoring sessions with individual students.",
    "In one such session, participants were asked to complete a conversation with the tutor bot in the context of educational reform."
